<TITLE> Rod import goes VAT-free </TITLE>
<TEXT>
 Dhaka, June 9 (bdnews24.com)  The finance adviser has proposed withdrawal of 15 percent VAT on imports of mild-steel bar and rod. Finance adviser AB Mirza Azizul Islam Monday also proposed specific duty on raw materials (meltable and re-rollable scrap) for steel products used in the construction sector. In his budget speech, he said the proposals were meant to stabilise domestic market in the backdrop of recent abnormal price escalation on the international market. bd
